<p><font size="2" color="#FFFFFF" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"><a name="pinball"></a><font size="+1" color="#FFcc33">Pinball 
  Machine:</font></font></p>
<blockquote> 
  <p><font size="2" color="#FFFFFF" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif">The 
    ROLLERCOASTER TYCOON pinball machine takes the most exciting elements of the 
    Infogrames' PC game and incorporates them into the fast interactive 3-D world 
    of the pinball playfield. The playfield consists of 4 roller coasters, including 
    &quot;The Flying Ghost,&quot; &quot;The Flying Turns,&quot; an inverted ramp 
    coaster called &quot;The Chicago Loop,&quot; and &quot;The Rocket,&quot; a 
    coaster that blasts the ball almost to the playfield glass before sending 
    it on a wild ride around the playfield. Other rides and features include: 
    the &quot;Scrambled Eggs&quot; spinning ride, the pop bumper Bumper Cars, 
    and the hysterical &quot;Dunk the Dummy&quot; side attraction. Designed in 
    the true spirit of the PC game, the ROLLERCOASTER TYCOON pinball machine is 
    a great ride and great fun for everyone.<br>
    <br>
